{"tid":2061365,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員提台灣防衛法 維持美軍阻中國武力犯台能力","createTime":"2020-06-12T10:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T12:18:14.000Z","uid":254183,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"982a65c909b9171d2c8ad748af4406cb7dcf336a","tid":2061365,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006120005.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202006120005.aspx&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjP2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=6e17ddb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006120005.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n這份16頁的法案草案的立法目的，在維持美軍阻止中國對台灣與其他目的造成既成事實的能力。草案定義的「既成事實」（fait accompli）是指中國在美軍尚未作出有效反應前，利用軍事力量奪取台灣控制權，同時說服美軍相信採取應對行動將非常困難或得付出高成本。<br />\n<br />\n草案國會意見指出，若中國能強迫台灣與中國統一，特別是透過軍事力量達成時，美國維護自由開放印太區域的能力將受到嚴重損害。台灣命運與包括美國在內的印太國家命運緊密相連。"},{"pid":"1d4b1447c8fca3c30b0c968c52366ece0b48cf61","tid":2061365,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"而家究竟有幾多條台灣,香港,新彊,西藏法律?"},{"pid":"04cb1348ebe1d7979da0e5faf0832614581f9d8a","tid":2061365,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b468be02b3a0944befd93e5d2e344c3b51e006bf","tid":2061365,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">China Joe 表示：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ec91b49a28fc85b30e8c7b5eb2129fe18bdb2f9d","tid":2061365,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d4b1447c8fca3c30b0c968c52366ece0b48cf61","tid":2061365,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:33:57.000Z","m